'''Nutmeat''' was a [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]] paste made from crushed [[ettel nut]]s. It was commonly served as a separate course during meals. Nutmeat was sweet, nutritious and high in calories. Because of this last property, it was occasionally part of a [[Soldier/Legends|soldier's]] survival [[Ration pack/Legends|rations]].

==Appearances==
